==Spanish==
===Etymology===
Latin ''[[opinari]]''
===Verb===
'''opinar'''
#to [[think]]; to be of the opinion
#:Creo que eso sería mejor, ¿y tú qué opinas? &ndash; I think that would be better; what do you think?
#to express one's [[opinion]]; to [[opine]]
#:Todos tenemos el derecho de opinar &ndash; We all have the right to express our opinions.

